name: The Girl Who Has A Name Dada

metadata.name: Freedom Of Confinement
metadata.description:
(The Girl Who Has a Name Dada. Part 0)
2022

When you find yourself physically or psychologically confined, you always have the choice to become free. 
By gaining new knowledge, acquiring new skills, your future will always be in your hands, regardless of external factors.


Author: Dada Aleksandrova 
3D animation @MrCubiqs
